name: the agony in kaleidoscope
description:
The Blink Projek
These collectibles are simple animations, with super macro focus on one eye blinking.

Zooming to an eye and pupil shows the window of one's consciousness
and of its soul which is hard to see outside.

Every personality carries a lot of loads from the past and manifests them in the present. By the counts of blink, time shows its superiority and knows the limit when the blinking ends. When the person stops blinking, it is uncertain if the person will reach a destination where there is no such thing as blinking, or if blinking will start all over again.
